lead_paragraph: Jacob Peterson scored and Benny Feilhaber had an assist to help Sporting Kansas City beat the Portland Timbers 1-0 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Peterson, Feilhaber Lead Sporting KC to 1-0 Win Over Timber
